quran[24{c,v,t}:
55,17,wohi dono mashriqon aur dono maghrabon ka maalik ( hai )
55,18,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,19,isi ne do darya rawan kiye jo aapas mein mlitay hain
55,20,dono mein aik aarr hai ke ( is se ) tajawaz nahi kar saktay
55,21,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,22,dono daryaaon se moti aur mongay nikaltay hain
55,23,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,24,aur jahaaz bhi isi ke hain jo darya mein pahoron ki terhan ounchay kharray hotay hain
55,25,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,26,jo ( makhlooq ) zameen par hai sab ko fanaa hona hai
55,27,aur tumahray perwar-digaar hi ki zaat (ba barkaat ) jo sahib jalal vazmt hai baqi rahay gi
55,28,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,29,aasman aur zameen mein jitne log hain sab isi se mangte hain. woh har roz kaam mein masroof rehta hai
55,30,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,31,ae dono jmaato! hum anqareeb tumhari taraf mutwajjah hotay hain
55,32,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,33,ae giroh jin o ins agar tumhe qudrat ho ke aasman aur zameen ke kinaroon se nikal jao to nikal jao. aur zor ke siwa tum nikal saknay hi ke nahi
55,34,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,35,tum par aag ke sholay aur dhuwan chore diya jaye ga to phir tum muqaabla nah krsko ge
55,36,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,37,phir jab aasman phatt kar tail ki tilchat ki terhan gulaabii hojaye ga ( to ) woh kaisa holnaak din hoga
55,38,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
55,39,is roz nah to kisi ensaan se is ke gunaaho ke baray mein prssh ki jaye gi aur nah kisi jin se
55,40,to tum apne perwar-digaar ki kon kon si Nemat ko jhutlao ge ?
